http://git.gnome.org/browse/xchat-gnome/commit/?id=23aa5dd1a3033c0badd750bedea8ba1b7a677a74
added some "GTK_CHECK_VERSION (2, 23, 0)" check, but it use (2, 16, 0) in some
places, which seems wrong.
